When the litigants are before you, see them as criminals.

And when the litigants have taken their leave, see them as innocent, should they have accepted the decision.|multiline=y|source=[[Pirkei Avot]] 1:8<ref name="PirkeiAvot">{{Cite book |title=Mishnah, Seder Nezikin, Tractate Avot |publisher=Wikisource|url=https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Translation:Mishnah/Seder_Nezikin/Tractate_Avot}}</ref>}}

