'''Legal''' '''status''' is the position held by something or someone with regard to law.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://definitions.uslegal.com/l/legal-status/|title=Legal Status Law and Legal Definition {{!}} USLegal, Inc.|last=Inc.|first=US Legal,|website=definitions.uslegal.com|language=en-US|access-date=2017-02-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://thelawdictionary.org/status/|title=What is STATUS? definition of STATUS (Black's Law Dictionary)|website=thelawdictionary.org|language=en-US|access-date=2017-02-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.vocabulary.com/dictionary/legal%20status|title=legal status - Dictionary Definition|work=Vocabulary.com|access-date=2017-02-27}}</ref> It is a set of privileges, obligations, powers or restrictions that a person or thing has which are encompassed in or declared by legislation.

